{{#freestyle-subsection name='c-input-radio' section=section}}

  {{#freestyle-annotation}}
    <p>Extends: <em>c-form-component-class</em></p>
    <p>We're demonstrating the <em>c-input-radio</em> element in these states: <em>default</em>, <em>focus</em> and <em>disabled</em>.</p>
    <p>The <em>c-input-radio</em> component exists in these variants: <em>horizontal</em>, <em>vertical</em> and <em>nested</em>.</p>
    <p>Currently the visible element is a default browser rendering. In the light of progressive enhancement, we will replace the standard visual style with our own at a later stage.</p>
    <p>The element options are set through the <code>items</code> attribute which accepts an <em>array</em>.</p>
  {{/freestyle-annotation}}

  {{!-- NOTE: Don't use the same model.radioOptions index twice, or you'll get a duplicated ID error --}}

  {{#freestyle-collection title='c-input-radio layout' defaultKey='all' inline=false as |collection|}}

    {{#freestyle-variant collection=collection key='horizontal'}}
      {{#freestyle-usage 'c-input-radio-horizontal' title='horizontal' usageTitle=labels.usage.title}}
        {{c-input-radio
          items=model.selectOptions
          label="A Label"
          layout="horizontal"
        }}
      {{/freestyle-usage}}
    {{/freestyle-variant}}

    {{#freestyle-variant collection=collection key='vertical'}}
      {{#freestyle-usage 'c-input-radio-vertical' title='vertical' usageTitle=labels.usage.title}}
        {{c-input-radio
          items=model.selectOptions
          label="A Label"
          layout="vertical"
        }}
      {{/freestyle-usage}}
    {{/freestyle-variant}}

    {{#freestyle-variant collection=collection key='nested'}}
      {{#freestyle-usage 'c-input-radio-nested' title='nested' usageTitle=labels.usage.title}}
        {{c-input-radio
          items=model.selectOptions
          label="A Label"
          layout="nested"
      }}
      {{/freestyle-usage}}
    {{/freestyle-variant}}

  {{/freestyle-collection}}



